Wuhan new coronavirus epidemic prevention information collection platform

In response to the outbreak of the new coronavirus in Wuhan in early 2020, this project aims to collect information from hospitals, hotels, factories, logistics, donations, donations, prevention, treatment, and dynamics, and uniformly collect and release them for the various parties Information exchange and effective deployment of social resources.

This warehouse is the main data warehouse. All data is automatically submitted and imported by the script. Please do not directly submit data information in this warehouse. For specific data submission channels, please refer to this document.

Collaboration process

In order to facilitate everyone's collaboration, this platform builds the following collaboration process

img

Except for the manual review of information, the other parts are automated and should not require manual intervention.

