Data submission

The information collected by this platform includes the following types of data submission, please report and fill in separately.

This platform uses graphite documents to collect data information, and the script periodically synchronizes data to the warehouse. Please do not modify the data files directly in the warehouse.

Due to the large number of participants, the editing rights of all personnel are not open. Please fill out the application here, and will direct invitations to specific forms for information entry.

